== Events == * {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1161|ja|1161|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|September 24|ja|9月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Due to a smallpox outbreak, the era name was changed from {{ill|Eiryaku|ja|Eireki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 15th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1702|ja|1702|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yokoi Yayuu|ja|横井也有|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a haiku poet († {{ill|1783|ja|1783|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kanpo|ja|寛保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1742|ja|1742|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 2|ja|10月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Arakida Tsunemasa|ja|荒木田経雅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a kokugakusha († {{ill|1805|ja|1805|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
