{{Lunisolar September}} 
'''September 4''' is the 4th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1161|ja|1161|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|September 24|ja|9月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Due to a smallpox outbreak, the era name was changed from {{ill|Eiryaku|ja|Eireki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  to {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births ==
* {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 15th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1702|ja|1702|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yokoi Yayuu|ja|横井也有|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a haiku poet († {{ill|1783|ja|1783|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kanpo|ja|寛保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1742|ja|1742|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 2|ja|10月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Arakida Tsunemasa|ja|荒木田経雅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a kokugakusha († {{ill|1805|ja|1805|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Shōtoku (Japan)|ja|正徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1715|ja|1715|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 1|ja|10月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Koyama Ryōshi|ja|小山良師|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an officer (ashigarutō) of the Akō Domain (* {{ill|1648|ja|1648|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1722|ja|1722|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Konoe Motoki|ja|近衛基熙|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a court noble (* {{ill|1648|ja|1648|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1820|ja|1820|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Urakami Gyokudō|ja|浦上玉堂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a painter of literary style (* {{ill|1745|ja|1745|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

