{{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 4''' is the 4th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1161|ja|1161|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|September 24|ja|9月24日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – Due to a smallpox outbreak, the era name was changed from {{ill|Eiryaku|ja|Eireki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . == Births == * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 15th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1702|ja|1702|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Yokoi Yayuu|ja|横井也有|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a haiku poet († {{ill|1783|ja|1783|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kanpo|ja|寛保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1742|ja|1742|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 2|ja|10月2日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Arakida Tsunemasa|ja|荒木田経雅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a kokugakusha († {{ill|1805|ja|1805|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Shōtoku (Japan)|ja|正徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1715|ja|1715|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 1|ja|10月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Koyama Ryōshi|ja|小山良師|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , an officer (ashigarutō) of the Akō Domain (* {{ill|1648|ja|1648|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1722|ja|1722|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Konoe Motoki|ja|近衛基熙|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a court noble (* {{ill|1648|ja|1648|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1820|ja|1820|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Urakami Gyokudō|ja|浦上玉堂|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a painter of literary style (* {{ill|1745|ja|1745|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
