'''September 4''' is the 4th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|qq=}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōhō|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1161|ja|1161|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1161|qq=}}  {{ill|September 24|ja|9月24日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September 24|qq=}} ） – Due to a smallpox outbreak, the era name was changed from {{ill|Eiryaku|ja|Eireki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eiryaku|qq=}}  to {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōhō|qq=}} .
== Births ==
* {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=}} 15th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1702|ja|1702|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1702|qq=}}  {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 24|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Yokoi Yayuu|ja|横井也有|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokoi Yayuu|qq=}} , a haiku poet († {{ill|1783|ja|1783|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1783|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Kanpo|ja|寛保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanpo|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1742|ja|1742|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1742|qq=}}  {{ill|October 2|ja|10月2日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 2|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Arakida Tsunemasa|ja|荒木田経雅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Arakida Tsunemasa|qq=}} , a kokugakusha († {{ill|1805|ja|1805|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1805|qq=}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Shōtoku (Japan)|ja|正徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōtoku (Japan)|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1715|ja|1715|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1715|qq=}}  {{ill|October 1|ja|10月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 1|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Koyama Ryōshi|ja|小山良師|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koyama Ryōshi|qq=}} , an officer (ashigarutō) of the Akō Domain (* {{ill|1648|ja|1648|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1648|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1722|ja|1722|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1722|qq=}}  {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 13|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Konoe Motoki|ja|近衛基熙|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konoe Motoki|qq=}} , a court noble (* {{ill|1648|ja|1648|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1648|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1820|ja|1820|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1820|qq=}}  {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 10|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Urakami Gyokudō|ja|浦上玉堂|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Urakami Gyokudō|qq=}} , a painter of literary style (* {{ill|1745|ja|1745|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1745|qq=}} ).

